name: Hello Darkness My Old Friend
description:
First erg workout in 4 years 😭

2 x 10’ at former 60’ pace had me cooked LOL but that was expected

Left achilles was feelin’ a little tender - didn’t wanna push that with a run so figured I’d just hop on this ol’ friend of mine & see what happens. 

Didn’t have an actual workout planned out, figured I’d feel it out hence the “just row”’type of memory screen haha - planning to mix these in maybe once a week or so once it gets real cold & there’ll inevitably be days where I don’t wanna run due to ❄️ 🥶
